@FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress = http://localhost:5297

### Liveness — basic health probe
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Ingestion worker health (returns HTTP 503 when unhealthy)
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/health/worker
Accept: application/json

### Latest N wide telemetry snapshots for one machine (count = 1..100)
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/v1/telemetry/EQP-001/latest?count=5
Accept: application/json

### Latest normalized per-sensor readings, optionally filtered by sensor type
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/v1/sensors/EQP-001/readings?count=10&sensorType=Pressure
Accept: application/json

### Fleet roster — one rolled-up summary row per machine that has reported
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/v1/machines
Accept: application/json

### Per-machine statistics over a rolling window (windowMinutes defaults to 60)
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/v1/telemetry/EQP-001/stats?windowMinutes=60
Accept: application/json

### Fleet-wide health snapshot over a rolling window (windowMinutes defaults to 60)
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/api/v1/fleet/status?windowMinutes=60
Accept: application/json

### Prometheus metrics
GET {{FactoryIoT.Presentation_HostAddress}}/metrics
